            <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Try FreeModel</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">FreeModel offers China-direct access to DeepSeek V3/R1, GPT-4o, Claude 3.5, and 50+ models through a single OpenAI-compatible API endpoint.</p>
              <a href="https://freemodel.dev/invite/FRE-7a3b6220" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:underline break-all">freemodel.dev/invite/FRE-7a3b6220</a>
            </div>
